name: Happy
description: I'm Mia and I made this picture with a lot of creativity and I want you to buy this picture so that you can support me and my family. I'm 7 years old and yet my dad made me my own gallery at Hic et Nunc. This picture describes a girl named Conni - she goes for a walk and meets an alien. But not an ordinary alien like you know it, but a huge one. Suddenly a girl comes by with a rocket backpack. She is in a bubble that moves the way the girl wants it to be. The bubble has a heart shape. Your Mia.
